version of this software is available at
http://www.pablotron.org/software/joystick-ruby/

Introduction
============
Joystick-Ruby is a Ruby binding that allows you to to read joystick
devices in Linux with an event-driven interface.

Installing Joystick-Ruby
========================
Execute the following commands:

# ruby extconf.rb
# make && su -c 'make install'

